 </div><div type="translation" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="fr">
            <p>Theudôros fils d'Hagèsitratos.</p>
         </div><div type="translation" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="en">
            <p>Theudoros son of Hagesistratos.</p>
         </div><div type="translation" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="it">
            <p>Theudoros figlio di Hagesistratos.</p>
         </div><div type="commentary">
                
                <p>The base is very similar to <ref type="inscription" source="#IGCyr2">IGCyr085800</ref> and both have been found during building works for the new town of Shahat;
                    the first editors thus supposed that they belonged to the same family-tomb.</p>
	<p/>
